        <name>addr</name>
        <qualifiedname>i3c_ccc_address::addr</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>For SETDASA, Static Address to be assigned as Dynamic Address.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>For SETNEWDA, new Dynamic Address to be assigned.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>For SETGRPA, new Group Address to be set.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>For GETACCCR, the correct address of Secondary Controller.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>For SETDATA, SETNEWDA and SETGRPA, the address is left-shift by 1, and bit[0] is always 0.</para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>For SET GETACCCR, the address is left-shift by 1, and bit[0] is the calculated odd parity bit. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
        </inbodydescription>
