    </sectiondef>
    <briefdescription>
<para>Payload for a single device address. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This is used for:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>SETDASA (Set Dynamic Address from Static Address)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>SETNEWDA (Set New Dynamic Address)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>SETGRPA (Set Group Address)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>GETACCCR (Get Accept Controller Role)</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>Note that the target address is encoded within struct <ref refid="structi3c__ccc__target__payload" kindref="compound">i3c_ccc_target_payload</ref> instead of being encoded in this payload. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
